  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250580/extras/d75f294d8098841b7274b0fc6de35d77.avif?t=1593028220\" width=600 height=337 /></span><br><br>Paranautical Activity combines the classic FPS action of games like Doom and Quake, with the randomness and difficulty of modern roguelikes like Binding of Isaac and Spelunky.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250580/extras/a45a2ae09a1ed666f5edad53471dd033.avif?t=1593028220\" width=580 height=271 /></span><br>-Unique FPS/Roguelike combination<br>-Procedurally generated levels<br>-Impossibly fast gameplay<br>-Hidden levels<br>-Over 100 items<br>-40+ enemies<br>-Ridiculous bosses‏<br>-Kick ass Dubstep soundtrack<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250580/extras/96d352806f08c6d46d3d8f04f1e02340.avif?t=1593028220\" width=629 height=305 /></span><br>The Deluxe Atonement Edition includes the following<br>-Developer footage & commentary, from prototype to pre alpha to full release! <br>-The Seafarers Guide; A pro guide with a nautical twist. Consult the pro guide to become the leanest, baddest, mostest bestest Paranautical Activity player you can be. <br>-1 new level type, 1 new weapon and 1 new item.<br>-Wallpapers baby!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250580/extras/d75f294d8098841b7274b0fc6de35d77.avif?t=1593028220\" width=600 height=337 /></span><br><br>Paranautical Activity combines the classic FPS action of games like Doom and Quake, with the randomness and difficulty of modern roguelikes like Binding of Isaac and Spelunky.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250580/extras/a45a2ae09a1ed666f5edad53471dd033.avif?t=1593028220\" width=580 height=271 /></span><br>-Unique FPS/Roguelike combination<br>-Procedurally generated levels<br>-Impossibly fast gameplay<br>-Hidden levels<br>-Over 100 items<br>-40+ enemies<br>-Ridiculous bosses‏<br>-Kick ass Dubstep soundtrack<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/250580/extras/96d352806f08c6d46d3d8f04f1e02340.avif?t=1593028220\" width=629 height=305 /></span><br>The Deluxe Atonement Edition includes the following<br>-Developer footage & commentary, from prototype to pre alpha to full release! <br>-The Seafarers Guide; A pro guide with a nautical twist. Consult the pro guide to become the leanest, baddest, mostest bestest Paranautical Activity player you can be. <br>-1 new level type, 1 new weapon and 1 new item.<br>-Wallpapers baby!",
